g, model calls, vector DB calls, and runtime/network effects; mocks would mask real latency regressions. Rejection gate: Agentic rejected because the assertion is latency SLO, not model output quality/decision correctness; Workflow rejected because no multi-step agentic decision quality is being evaluated.","test_description":"Run production-like API load tests over real HTTP with real dependencies in a staging environment, collect end-to-end latencies, and assert median response time is under 2.0s.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.01,"Integration":0.1,"System":0.78,"Agentic":0.1,"Workflow":0.01}}]}
